Class AStarCamvitChoiceRouting

  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    com.graphhopper.routing.RoutingAlgorithm, AlternativeRoutesRoutingAlgorithm
    public class AStarCamvitChoiceRouting
extends AbstractCamvitChoiceRouting
    Calculates alternative routes next to the best route, by using bidirectional AStar as routing engine and 'camvit choice routing' afterwards to determine alternative routes.
